Method Detail

test_2_1_19_1_VxmlDialog

public void test_2_1_19_1_VxmlDialog()
                              throws java.lang.Exception
Basic testing of a VxmlDialog - Accept "unsupported" response.

Create, prepare and start a VxmlDialog joined to a NetworkConnection.
Implementations not supporting voicexml will throw an early exception on the VxmlDialog creation, and the testcase will terminate with success in that case.
Include calls to prepare(), processSdpOffer(SDPoffer), start().
The events VxmlDialogEvent.PREPARED, VxmlDialogEvent.STARTED and VxmlDialogEvent.EXITED are checked.

Throws:
java.lang.Exception
